		explode nano5 type SMOKE | FALL;
		explode nano6 type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | SMOKE | FALL;
		explode head4 type FIRE | SMOKE | FALL;
		explode nano7 type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | SMOKE | FALL;
		explode nano8 type SMOKE | FALL;
		explode pad type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | SMOKE | FALL;
